<HEADLINE>
RANGERS' COOL-DOWN CONTINUES IN LOSS TO TWINS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By T.R. SULLIVAN 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
 
 
 
 
