<P>
   FOOD-COLUMN-OWEN (Undated) _ It could be that Toronto was named
the world's most livable city because a resident or visitor is
never more than half a block away from a sausage stand or a
doughnut shoppe. You can hardly get more livable than that.
</P>
<P>
