<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-28 18:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8149 &Cx1f; tth-z
r d BC-FOOD-OWEN-COLUMN-SPI &LR;      05-28 0886
