<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-28 20:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8219 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-COMMENCEMENT-ADDRESSE     05-28 1221
